      "woman": "The women born under the Sign Sagittarius are truthful, idealistic, and have a great sense of humour. They wish to learn things from their own experience, instead of relying on second-hand opinions. This is why they like to meet different people, share experiences, and experiment with different things. Read on to find out more about the Sagittarius women. Also, try the Birth Chart based personalised service Life Prediction – Overview.\nThe women born under this Sign are very curious and have a philosophical bent of mind. They are capable of doing many things, are charming people, and enjoy life as it comes. For any specific aspect that you wish to know more about, right away Talk to an Astrologer!\nWomen of this Sign are not very sensitive, but are broad-minded. When they are given feedback, they take it seriously and work on improving themselves."
